Class ExtendedLinkElement

java.lang.Object
  xbrlcore.xlink.ExtendedLinkElement

Direct Known Subclasses:
Locator, Resource
public abstract class ExtendedLinkElement
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

This class is an abstract super class for possible extended link elements, namely locators and resources.

Author:
Daniel Hamm

Method Detail

equals

public boolean equals(java.lang.Object obj)
Checks whether two extended link elements are equal. This is true if and only if:
- both must be either locators or resources
- both have the same label attribute
- both have the same role attribute
- both have the same title attribute
- both have the same id attribute
- both belong to the same extended link role

Overrides:
equals in class java.lang.Object
Parameters:
obj - The object the current ExtendedLinkElement is checked against.
Returns:
True if both objects are equal, false otherwise.
